##Import Terraform Providers Modules & Plugins##
terrafornm init

##Provide code overview of what will be changed/deployed##
terraform plan
terraform plan -target [specified resource(s)]

##Apply code to create infrastructure##
terraform apply 
terraform apply -target [specified resource(s)]

##Destroy created infrastructure##
terraform destroy
terraform destroy -target [specified resource(s)]

##Refresh current state of infrastructure [check TFstate file for more]##
terraform refresh

##Use to specify and deactivate code## 
